prompts.frontCover: A vibrant, dynamic comic book cover for a birthday card. In the center, a charming cartoon-style character, looking utterly overwhelmed but with a hilarious, wide-eyed, joyful expression, is being comically buried under an enormous, teetering pile of brightly wrapped birthday presents. The gifts are all different shapes and sizes, with exaggerated, colorful wrapping paper featuring polka dots, stripes, and stars. A few ribbons are comically unspooling into the air. The background is a classic comic book action scene with a bright yellow sunburst explosion pattern. Bold, black ink lines define the character and the presents, with flat, vibrant colors and Ben-Day dot patterns for shading. In the center, layered over the image in a dynamic, slightly angled comic book-style speech bubble, is the text "Hope your birthday is a BLAST!" written in a beautiful, readable, and slightly playful handwritten cursive script. The overall composition is energetic, fun, and eye-catching.
